ent-Scp096CryOut = emit mournful scream
    .desc = Through your tears, you let out a scream capable of damaging nearby visible structures. Use it to create cracks in your containment cell and escape.
ent-Scp096FaceSkinRip = tear off face skin
    .desc = You gradually tear the skin from your face, carving away your hated self. Once your face becomes an indistinguishable bloody mess, you will gain the ability to open blast doors, airlocks, and attack humans. And no one will be able to see your face anymore, unless it regenerates!
ent-Scp096SitDown = sit down
    .desc = You sit down in a sorrowful pose.
